snippet.title: SpellForce: Heroes & Magic // Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now!
Android: http://bit.ly/SpellForce
iOS Appstore: http://bit.ly/SpellForceHM

Craft your fantasy empire in this turn-based strategy game!

Time for a new turn on the critically acclaimed SpellForce-Series. The epic fantasy saga is finally coming to mobile devices, offering a whole new angle to the franchise. 

● CRAFT YOUR FANTASY EMPIRE
● EXPLORE NEW LANDS
● BATTLE YOUR ENEMIES
● EVOLVE YOUR SOLDIERS

Pre-register available in the Apple AppStore and Google Play!

#HandyGames #SpellForceHM #SFHM #HexGames #Tactics #Strategy #SpellForce
